data.description: Price reduced to make a good deal. Great location! This tucked away property is minutes from the Seward Highway with easy access to anywhere in town. Fireplace anchors the vaulted ceiling in the gathering room that is great for hosting, and family events. Deck upstairs makes for perfect morning coffee. Dining area right off the kitchen is great for family time meals.Spacious master bedroom upstairs, and bedrooms downstairs have their own bathroom and living space.
